Frontend sends request
        ↓
index.js (server)
        ↓
routes/auth.js
        ↓
authController.js
        ↓
DB (PostgreSQL)
        ↓
Response sent back


Protected Route Flow


Request with token
        ↓
authMiddleware
        ↓
Token verified
        ↓
Access granted

User adds items → Redis cart
        ↓
User clicks checkout
        ↓
Create Order in DB
        ↓
Create Razorpay order
        ↓
User pays (test mode)
        ↓
Verify payment
        ↓
Mark order as PAID + clear cart

Guest User
   ↓
localStorage Cart

Logged-in User
   ↓
Frontend CartContext
   ↓ API Calls
Backend Cart Routes
   ↓
Redis